    "steps": [
      {
        "id": 1039279,
        "guid": "CF14B470FF3D11EAA81873B0499D24C8",
        "previous_id": 0,
        "previous_guid": null,
        "section": "<p>Discuss Sample Types</p>",
        "section_color": "#A492FF",
        "section_duration": 0,
        "is_substep": false,
        "step": "\nReview SalivaDirect for sample processing protocol: [https://www.protocols.io/view/salivadirect-rna-extraction-free-sars-cov-2-diagno-bkjgkujw?step=11](https://www.protocols.io/view/salivadirect-rna-extraction-free-sars-cov-2-diagno-bkjgkujw?step=11)",
        "data": null,
        "protocol_id": 42488,
        "case_id": 0,
        "critical_ids": "",
        "duration": 0,
        "original_id": 0,
        "number": "1",
        "cases": [],
        "critical": null
      },
      {
        "id": 1039384,
        "guid": "D13EEDD0FF4511EAA81873B0499D24C8",
        "previous_id": 1039279,
        "previous_guid": "CF14B470FF3D11EAA81873B0499D24C8",
        "section": "<p>Inset Well Plate in Benchling Lab Notebook</p>",
        "section_color": "#94EBFF",
        "section_duration": 0,
        "is_substep": false,
        "step": "Open your Benchling Lab Notebook and insert &#34;Lab 4&#34; with heading &#34;H1&#34;. Add pertinent links to protocols like the SalivaDirect protocol. ",
        "data": null,
        "protocol_id": 42488,
        "case_id": 0,
        "critical_ids": "",
        "duration": 0,
        "original_id": 0,
        "number": "2",
        "cases": [],
        "critical": null
      },
      {
        "id": 1039398,
        "guid": "3ADCE7C0FF4A11EAA81873B0499D24C8",
        "previous_id": 1039384,
        "previous_guid": "D13EEDD0FF4511EAA81873B0499D24C8",
        "section": "<p>Inset Well Plate in Benchling Lab Notebook</p>",
        "section_color": "#94EBFF",
        "section_duration": 0,
        "is_substep": false,
        "step": "We need to set up the format for our experiment in a 96-well plate. \n\nAdd a 96-well well plate by selecting &#34;Insert&gt;Well plate&gt;96-well plate&#34;. \n[image.png]](https://content.protocols.io/public/ff5cc910650017d1b800ee5dd2e2daaffb2556d2ce15802adf29d20349e67ffa/ck6ses8e.png)\nAdd a 96-w &#34;Well plate&#34; in Benchling. \n",
        "data": null,
        "protocol_id": 42488,
        "case_id": 0,
        "critical_ids": "",
        "duration": 0,
        "original_id": 0,
        "number": "3",
        "cases": [],
        "critical": null
      },
      {
        "id": 1039399,
        "guid": "BDBB6860FF4A11EAA81873B0499D24C8",
        "previous_id": 1039398,
        "previous_guid": "3ADCE7C0FF4A11EAA81873B0499D24C8",
        "section": "<p>Inset Well Plate in Benchling Lab Notebook</p>",
        "section_color": "#94EBFF",
        "section_duration": 0,
        "is_substep": false,
        "step": "Add saliva samples 1 to 4, the no-template control and positive control using plasmid &#34;pEX-A128-nCoV_CD&#34;. Make sure to &#34;@-mention&#34; the plasmid &#34;pEX-A128-nCoV_CD&#34; located in the BSCI:414 directory. Do not copy this to a new folder. \n\n[image.png]](https://content.protocols.io/public/ff5cc910650017d1b800ee5dd2e2daaffb2556d2ce15802adf29d20349e67ffa/ck6ves8e.png)\n96-well plate outline in Benchling. \n",
        "data": null,
        "protocol_id": 42488,
        "case_id": 0,
        "critical_ids": "",
        "duration": 0,
        "original_id": 0,
        "number": "4",
        "cases": [],
        "critical": null
      },
      {
        "id": 1039417,
        "guid": "3F3CAD80FF4C11EAA81873B0499D24C8",
        "previous_id": 1039399,
        "previous_guid": "BDBB6860FF4A11EAA81873B0499D24C8",
        "section": "<p>Add qPCR Schedule to Lab Notebook</p>",
        "section_color": "#84CE84",
        "section_duration": 0,
        "is_substep": false,
        "step": "Add a 2x7 table using &#34;Insert&gt;Table&#34;. \n\nCopy the qPCR schedule from Step 11 in SalivaDirect into the table . Use the values from the &#34;NEB Luna&#34; kit. \n\nAdd a &#34;Saliva Sample&#34; row containing 5ul.\n\nAdd a &#34;TOTAL&#34; row at the bottom and ensure reagents total 20ul. \n\n\n\n[image.png]](https://content.protocols.io/public/ff5cc910650017d1b800ee5dd2e2daaffb2556d2ce15802adf29d20349e67ffa/ck6yes8e.png)\nAdd a 2x7 table. \n\n[image.png]](https://content.protocols.io/public/ff5cc910650017d1b800ee5dd2e2daaffb2556d2ce15802adf29d20349e67ffa/ck6wes8e.png)\nqPCR Schedule in Benchling. \n",
        "data": null,
        "protocol_id": 42488,
        "case_id": 0,
        "critical_ids": "",
        "duration": 0,
        "original_id": 0,
        "number": "5",
        "cases": [],
        "critical": null
      }
